---
layout: post
title:  "Introduction to Trip Shift"
date:   2023-03-26 23:10:36 +2310
---

Welcome to Trip Shift, the industrial horror game that takes you on a mind-bending journey through an otherworldly clothes factory. Navigate through a series of strange and twisted tasks given to you by an unseen supervisor, all while battling the effects of powerful drugs that alter your perception and gameplay mechanics. Can you make it through the six surreal days and escape the factory before it's too late?
